HEADWORD: Tidbit
<hw>Tid"bit`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Tid</ets> +
<ets>bit</ets>.]</ety> <def>A delicate or tender piece of anything
eatable; a delicious morsel.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>titbit</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

